Datasource.Parameter: (SELECT way, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE landuse IN ('residential', 'commercial', 'retail')) AS data
(SELECT way FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE aeroway IN ('aerodrome') OR landuse IN ('industrial')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "leisure" IN ('park', 'playground', 'pitch', 'golf_course') OR landuse IN ('recreation_ground', 'grass', 'cemetery')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('wood', 'scrub') OR landuse IN ('forest')) AS data
( SELECT way, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural"='beach' AND (surface='sand' OR surface IS NULL) ) AS data

( SELECT way, waterway AS type FROM planet_osm_line WHERE waterway IN ('riverbank', 'river', 'canal', 'stream', 'ditch') AND tunnel IS NULL AND (layer NOT IN ('-2') OR layer IS NULL) UNION SELECT way, waterway AS type FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE waterway IN ('riverbank') ) as DATA
( SELECT way, way_area AS area, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('water', 'pond') OR landuse IN ('reservoir', 'basin') OR waterway IN ('pond') ) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('wetland')) AS data
( SELECT way FROM planet_osm_line WHERE waterway = 'weir' ) as DATA
(SELECT way FROM planet_osm_line WHERE route IN ('ferry') ) as DATA
(SELECT way, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('glacier')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE landuse IN ('military') OR military IN ('danger_area')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE leisure IN ('nature_reserve')) AS data

( SELECT way FROM planet_osm_line WHERE man_made='pier' AND (access<>'private' OR access IS NULL) UNION SELECT way FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE man_made='pier' AND (access<>'private' OR access IS NULL) ) as data
(SELECT way FROM planet_osm_line WHERE aeroway IN ('taxiway') ) as DATA
(SELECT way, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length FROM planet_osm_line WHERE aeroway IN ('runway') ) as DATA

(SELECT way, CASE WHEN "piste:difficulty" IN ('novice', 'easy') THEN 2 WHEN "piste:difficulty"='intermediate' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as difficulty FROM planet_osm_line WHERE "piste:type" = 'downhill' ) as DATA

(SELECT way, ST_Perimeter(way)::integer as boundary FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE barrier IN ('fence') AND (ST_Perimeter(way)::integer > 400) UNION SELECT way, ST_Perimeter(way)::integer as boundary FROM planet_osm_line WHERE barrier IN ('fence') AND (ST_Length(way)::integer > 400) ) AS data
( SELECT way, "building" AS type, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE building NOT IN ('0','false', 'no') ORDER BY ST_YMin(ST_Envelope(way)) DESC ) AS data
(SELECT way, ref FROM subway) as DATA

(SELECT way, highway AS type, CASE WHEN "name:de" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:de" WHEN "name:en" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:en" ELSE name END as name, tunnel, bridge, tracktype, oneway, CASE WHEN service='parking_aisle' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS parking_aisle, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length, CASE WHEN highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link') OR (highway IN('trunk') AND oneway IN ('yes')) THEN 90 WHEN highway IN ('trunk', 'trunk_link') THEN 100 WHEN highway IN ('primary', 'primary_link') THEN 60 WHEN highway IN ('secondary', 'secondary_link') THEN 50 WHEN highway IN ('tertiary', 'tertiary_link') THEN 40 WHEN highway IN ('road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1')) THEN 30 ELSE 0 END as prio FROM planet_osm_line WHERE (highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link', 'trunk', 'trunk_link', 'primary', 'primary_link', 'secondary', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') AND (service IS NULL OR service NOT IN ('parking_aisle')) OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1'))) AND (bridge IS NULL OR bridge NOT IN('yes')) AND tunnel IN('yes') ORDER BY prio DESC ) as DATA

(SELECT way, bicycle, CASE WHEN "mtb:scale"~E'^\\d+$' THEN "mtb:scale"::integer ELSE NULL END as mtbscale, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length FROM planet_osm_line WHERE highway IN ('path', 'footway', 'steps', 'bridleway') AND (bicycle IS NULL OR bicycle NOT IN('designated')) AND (bridge IS NULL OR bridge NOT IN('yes')) ) as DATA

(SELECT way, highway AS type, CASE WHEN "name:de" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:de" WHEN "name:en" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:en" ELSE name END as name, tunnel, bridge, tracktype, oneway, CASE WHEN service='parking_aisle' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS parking_aisle, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length, CASE WHEN highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link') OR (highway IN('trunk') AND oneway IN ('yes')) THEN 90 WHEN highway IN ('trunk', 'trunk_link') THEN 100 WHEN highway IN ('primary', 'primary_link') THEN 60 WHEN highway IN ('secondary', 'secondary_link') THEN 50 WHEN highway IN ('tertiary', 'tertiary_link') THEN 40 WHEN highway IN ('road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1')) THEN 30 ELSE 0 END as prio FROM planet_osm_line WHERE (highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link', 'trunk', 'trunk_link', 'primary', 'primary_link', 'secondary', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') AND (service IS NULL OR service IN ('parking_aisle')) OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1'))) AND (bridge IS NULL OR bridge NOT IN('yes')) AND (tunnel IS NULL OR tunnel NOT IN('yes')) ORDER BY prio DESC ) as DATA

(SELECT way, highway AS type, tracktype, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length, bicycle FROM planet_osm_line WHERE highway IN ('track') AND (tracktype IS NULL OR tracktype <> 'grade1') ) as DATA

( SELECT way, tunnel, railway as type FROM planet_osm_line WHERE (railway NOT IN ('abandoned', 'disused', 'razed', 'platform', 'construction', 'funicular', 'proposed')) AND (service IS NULL OR service NOT IN('yard')) AND attraction IS NULL ) as DATA

(SELECT way, bicycle, CASE WHEN "mtb:scale"~E'^\\d+$' THEN "mtb:scale"::integer ELSE NULL END as mtbscale, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length FROM planet_osm_line WHERE highway IN ('path', 'footway', 'steps', 'bridleway') AND (bicycle IS NULL OR bicycle NOT IN('designated')) AND (bridge IN('yes')) ) as DATA

(SELECT way, highway AS type, name, tracktype, tunnel, bridge, oneway, z_order, CASE WHEN service='parking_aisle' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS parking_aisle, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length, CASE WHEN highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link') OR (highway IN('trunk') AND oneway IN ('yes')) THEN 90 WHEN highway IN ('trunk', 'trunk_link') THEN 100 WHEN highway IN ('primary', 'primary_link') THEN 60 WHEN highway IN ('secondary', 'secondary_link') THEN 50 WHEN highway IN ('tertiary', 'tertiary_link') THEN 40 WHEN highway IN ('road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1')) THEN 30 ELSE 0 END as prio FROM planet_osm_line WHERE ( highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link', 'trunk', 'trunk_link', 'primary', 'primary_link', 'secondary', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1')) ) AND bridge IN('yes') AND (layer IS NULL OR layer <= '1') ORDER BY prio DESC) as DATA

(SELECT way, highway AS type, name, tracktype, tunnel, bridge, oneway, CASE WHEN service='parking_aisle' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS parking_aisle, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length, CASE WHEN highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link') OR (highway IN('trunk') AND oneway IN ('yes')) THEN 90 WHEN highway IN ('trunk', 'trunk_link') THEN 100 WHEN highway IN ('primary', 'primary_link') THEN 60 WHEN highway IN ('secondary', 'secondary_link') THEN 50 WHEN highway IN ('tertiary', 'tertiary_link') THEN 40 WHEN highway IN ('road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1')) THEN 30 ELSE 0 END as prio FROM planet_osm_line WHERE (highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link', 'trunk', 'trunk_link', 'primary', 'primary_link', 'secondary', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1'))) AND bridge IN('yes') AND (layer >= '2') ORDER BY prio DESC) as DATA
(SELECT way FROM planet_osm_line WHERE highway = 'cycleway' OR bicycle = 'designated') as DATA

(SELECT way, name, CASE WHEN attraction = 'summer_toboggan' THEN 'toboggan' ELSE aerialway END as type FROM planet_osm_line WHERE aerialway IN ('cable_car', 'chairlift', 'gondola', 'chair_lift', 'mixed_lift', 'goods') OR railway = 'funicular' OR attraction = 'summer_toboggan' ) as DATA
( SELECT DISTINCT ON(snapped) way, name, ele FROM ( SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(way, 400) as snapped, way, name, ele FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "natural" = 'peak' ) as tmp ) as DATA
(SELECT way FROM planet_osm_point WHERE power IN ('tower', 'station', 'sub_station')) as DATA
(SELECT way FROM planet_osm_line WHERE power IN ('line', 'minor_line')) as DATA

( SELECT DISTINCT ON(snapped) way, name, ele, CASE WHEN tourism IN ('alpine_hut', 'hotel') THEN tourism ELSE amenity END as type FROM ( SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(way, 300) as snapped, way, CASE WHEN "name:de" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:de" WHEN "name:en" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:en" ELSE name END as name, ele, amenity, tourism, CASE WHEN amenity = 'biergarten' THEN 10 ELSE 0 END as prio FROM planet_osm_point WHERE (amenity IN ('pub','fast_food','restaurant','bar','biergarten')) OR (tourism IN ('alpine_hut', 'hotel')) UNION SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(ST_Centroid(way), 300) as snapped, ST_Centroid(way) as way, CASE WHEN "name:de" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:de" WHEN "name:en" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:en" ELSE name END as name, ele, amenity, tourism, CASE WHEN amenity = 'biergarten' THEN 10 ELSE 0 END as prio FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE (amenity IN ('pub','fast_food','restaurant','bar','biergarten')) OR (tourism IN ('alpine_hut', 'hotel')) ) as tmp ORDER BY snapped, prio ) as data

( SELECT DISTINCT ON(snapped) way, name, ele, CASE WHEN tourism IN ('alpine_hut', 'hotel') THEN tourism ELSE amenity END as type FROM ( SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(way, 500) as snapped, way, name, ele, amenity, tourism, CASE WHEN amenity = 'biergarten' THEN 10 ELSE 0 END as prio FROM planet_osm_point WHERE (amenity IN ('pub','fast_food','restaurant','bar','biergarten')) OR (tourism IN ('alpine_hut', 'hotel')) UNION SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(ST_Centroid(way), 500) as snapped, ST_Centroid(way) as way, name, ele, amenity, tourism, CASE WHEN amenity = 'biergarten' THEN 10 ELSE 0 END as prio FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE (amenity IN ('pub','fast_food','restaurant','bar','biergarten')) OR (tourism IN ('alpine_hut', 'hotel')) ) as tmp ORDER BY snapped, prio ) as data

( SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(ST_Centroid(way),50) as way, CASE WHEN "name:de" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:de" WHEN "name:en" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:en" ELSE name END as name, railway as type, subway FROM planet_osm_point WHERE railway IN ('station', 'halt', 'tram_stop') ) as DATA

( SELECT DISTINCT ON(snapped) way, parking as type FROM ( SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(way, 200) as snapped, way, parking FROM planet_osm_point WHERE amenity='parking' AND (access<>'private' OR access IS NULL) UNION SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(ST_Centroid(way), 200) as snapped, ST_Centroid(way) as way, parking FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE amenity='parking' AND (access<>'private' OR access IS NULL) ) as tmp ) as data
(SELECT DISTINCT ON(snapped) way FROM (SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(way, 200) as snapped, way FROM planet_osm_point WHERE highway='bus_stop') as tmp ) as data

( SELECT DISTINCT ON(snapped) way FROM ( SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(way, 500) as snapped, way FROM planet_osm_point WHERE amenity='shelter' UNION SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(ST_Centroid(way), 500) as snapped, ST_Centroid(way) as way FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE amenity='shelter' ) as tmp ) as data

(SELECT way, highway AS type, ref, CHAR_LENGTH(ref) AS reflen FROM planet_osm_line WHERE (highway IN ('motorway', 'trunk', 'primary')) AND (bridge IS NULL OR bridge NOT IN('yes')) AND ref IS NOT NULL) as DATA

(SELECT way, way_area AS area, CASE WHEN "name:de" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:de" WHEN "name:en" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:en" ELSE name END as name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "leisure" IN ('park', 'playground', 'pitch', 'golf_course') OR landuse IN ('recreation_ground', 'grass', 'cemetery')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('wetland')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('wood', 'scrub') OR landuse IN ('forest')) AS data

(SELECT way, way_area AS area, CASE WHEN "name:de" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:de" WHEN "name:en" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:en" ELSE name END as name, ele FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('water', 'pond') OR waterway IN ('basin', 'canal', 'mill_pond', 'pond', 'riverbank', 'stream') OR landuse IN ('reservoir', 'basin')) AS data

( SELECT way, CASE WHEN "name:de" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:de" WHEN "name:en" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:en" ELSE name END as name, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length, waterway as type FROM planet_osm_line WHERE waterway IN ('river', 'canal', 'stream', 'ditch') AND tunnel IS NULL AND (layer NOT IN ('-2') OR layer IS NULL) AND name IS NOT NULL ) as data
( SELECT way, way_area AS area, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('glacier') AND name IS NOT NULL ) AS data
(SELECT way, route_name from planet_osm_line WHERE route='bicycle' AND route_name IS NOT NULL) as data

(SELECT way, way_area AS area, CASE WHEN "name:de" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:de" WHEN "name:en" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:en" ELSE name END as name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE aeroway IN ('aerodrome') OR landuse IN ('industrial')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE landuse IN ('military') OR military IN ('danger_area')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE leisure IN ('nature_reserve')) AS data

(SELECT DISTINCT ON(snapped) way, CASE WHEN leisure IN ('playground', 'water_park') THEN leisure WHEN sport IN('climbing') THEN sport WHEN geological IN('palaeontological_site') THEN geological ELSE tourism END as type, name FROM ( SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(way, 200) as snapped, way, tourism, geological, leisure, sport, CASE WHEN "name:de" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:de" WHEN "name:en" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:en" ELSE name END as name FROM planet_osm_point WHERE tourism IN ('viewpoint', 'information', 'zoo', 'aquarium', 'attraction', 'theme_park') OR leisure IN ('playground', 'water_park') OR sport IN('climbing') OR geological = 'palaeontological_site' UNION SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(ST_Centroid(way), 200) as snapped, ST_Centroid(way) as way, tourism, geological, leisure, sport, CASE WHEN "name:de" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:de" WHEN "name:en" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:en" ELSE name END as name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE tourism IN ('viewpoint', 'information', 'zoo', 'aquarium', 'attraction', 'theme_park') OR leisure IN ('playground', 'water_park') OR sport IN('climbing') OR geological = 'palaeontological_site' ) as tmp ) as data

( SELECT DISTINCT ON(snapped) way, type FROM ( SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(way, 200) as snapped, way, CASE WHEN "amenity" IN ('place_of_worship') AND "religion" IN ('christian') THEN 'church' WHEN "man_made" IN ('mast', 'tower', 'communications_tower', 'antenna') THEN 'tower' END as type FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "amenity" IN ('place_of_worship') AND "religion" IN ('christian') OR "man_made" IN ('mast', 'tower', 'communications_tower', 'antenna') UNION SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(ST_Centroid(way), 200) as snapped, ST_Centroid(way) as way, CASE WHEN "amenity" IN ('place_of_worship') AND "religion" IN ('christian') THEN 'church' WHEN "man_made" IN ('mast', 'tower', 'communications_tower', 'antenna') THEN 'tower' END as type FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "amenity" IN ('place_of_worship') AND "religion" IN ('christian') OR "man_made" IN ('mast', 'tower', 'communications_tower', 'antenna') ) as tmp ) as data
( SELECT way, shop as type FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE shop IN ('bicycle', 'supermarket') UNION SELECT way, shop as type FROM planet_osm_point WHERE shop IN ('bicycle', 'supermarket') ) as data

( SELECT way, CASE WHEN "name:de" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:de" WHEN "name:en" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:en" ELSE name END as name, ele, 100000 AS area, place, CASE WHEN population ~E'^\\d+$' THEN population::integer ELSE NULL END as pop FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "place" IN ('city', 'town', 'village', 'hamlet', 'suburb') AND name IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT way, CASE WHEN "name:de" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:de" WHEN "name:en" IS NOT NULL THEN "name:en" ELSE name END as name, ele, way_area AS area, place, CASE WHEN population ~E'^\\d+$' THEN population::integer ELSE NULL END as pop FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "place" IN ('city', 'town', 'village', 'hamlet', 'suburb') AND name IS NOT NULL ) as DATA
